==Objects==

Objects can be created, read, updated and deleted through the standard [http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2616 HTTP] methods (POST, GET, PUT, and DELETE respectively).

Their payloads complies with the [http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4627 JSON] standard format.

On creation, objects are given an "_id" by the service. If it handles conflict detection, they are given a "_rev" on each write action.

